                        <h5>Game DB</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Game DB has existed in one form or another since 2015.</li>
                            <li>Game DB is fully open sourced on <a href="https://github.com/gamedb" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.</li>
                            <li>Game DB gets all of its data from <a href="/steam-api">Steam APIs</a>, or <a href="https://github.com/SteamRE/SteamKit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SteamKit</a>.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h5>Apps (Games)</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Apps are updated instantly when the developer makes a change.</li>
                            <li>App review scores are calculated using <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Additive_smoothing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Additive Smoothing</a>.</li>
                            <li>App twitch counts only include the 100 streamers for that app.</li>
                            <li>App trend values currently use the algorithm taken from <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/a/49604913/472084" target="_blank" rel="noopener">this post</a>.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h5>Bundles</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Bundles are updated when an app in the bundle is updated.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h5>Changes</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Changes are updated instantly when the developer makes a change.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h5>Groups</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Groups are updated when a player in the group is updated, or when the group page is looked at. Limited to once per hour.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h5>Packages</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Packages are updated instantly when the developer makes a change.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h5>Players</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Players are updated when they are looked at, or automatically for donators.</li>
                            <li>Player ranks are calculated only from players on Game DB.</li>
                            <li>Player ranks are calculated started at midnight UTC and can take some time to finish processing.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h5>Sale</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Sales are updated when the app on sale is updated.</li>
                        </ul>

